  <features>
    <feature>LOCAL COOP: play with a friend and laugh your way to repeated failures and success</feature>
    <feature>5 PLAYABLE CREATURES: each adorable creature set will have you play slightly different with your friend. Each with an additional limitation than the previous</feature>
